<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>当 <code v-pre>bar</code> 函数执行的时候，<code v-pre>foo</code> 函数上下文已经被销毁了（亦即从执行上下文栈中被弹出），怎么还会读取到 <code v-pre>foo</code> 作用域下的 a 值呢？</p>
<p>当我们了解了具体的执行过程后，我们知道 <code v-pre>bar</code> 函数执行上下文维护了一个作用域链：</p>
<div class="language-js line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="js" data-title="js" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre v-pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E06C75">barContext</span><span style="--shiki-light:#0184BC;--shiki-dark:#56B6C2"> =</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF"> {</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#E45649;--shiki-dark:#E06C75">  Scope</span><span style="--shiki-light:#0184BC;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">:</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF"> [</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#E5C07B">AO</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">, </span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E5C07B">fooContext</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#E06C75">AO</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">, </span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E5C07B">globalContext</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#E06C75">VO</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">],</span></span>
